        // My previous patch was `match(CondVal, m_c_LogicalAnd(m_Specific(C1), m_Value(C2)))`.
        // So `m_c_LogicalAnd` was commutative! This caused it to match `m_LogicalAnd(C2, C1)`!
        // But in `nested-select.ll` it was matching something else that triggered regression.
      }
    }
  }
